<div id="page-title">

        <h1> Features overview </h1>
        <p>See how Fleetnext comes with tools and functionality to make fleet management easier and more productive.</p>

</div> <!-- /page-title -->


<div id="content">

        <div class="container">

                <div class="row">
                      <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                              <h3> <img src="/assets/allonline.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                              All your vehicles online
                              </h3>
                              <br/>
                              <p>
                              (a) Maintain profiles for every vehicle in the fleet with information about its acquisition details, vehicle make/model, license plate number, ownership details, engine number, chassis number, fuel type, disposal details etc <br/><br/>
                              (b) Scan and upload any relevant paperwork such as purchase invoices, registration certificates, warranty documents, manuals.
                              </p>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                                <a href="/assets/screenshots/vehicles.png">
                                <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/vehicles.png" />
                                </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                </div> <!-- /row -->
                <hr class="row-divider" />
                
                
                <div class="row">
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                             <a href="/assets/screenshots/documents.png">
                             <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/documents.png" />
                             </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                            <h3> <img src="/assets/alerts.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                            Renew vehicle documents on time
                            </h3>
                            <br/>
                            <p>(a) Simplify the management of documentation of your vehicles such as insurance certificates,taxes, fitness certificates, permits. <br/><br/>
                               (b) For each document, keep track of its expiry date, reference number, issuing authority. <br/><br/>
                               (c) Find documents that are due soon or have already expired. <br/><br/>
                               (d) Setup email notifications to remind you when a document is due for renewals.<br/><br/>
                            </p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                </div> <!-- /row -->
                <hr class="row-divider" />
                
                <div class="row">
                        <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                            <h3> <img src="/assets/repair.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                            Maintain vehicle service history
                            </h3>
                            <br/>
                            <p>
                              (a) Keep track of every vehicle's service history including workshop/garage repairs and preventive maintenance (PM) services. <br/><br/>
                              (b) Store important details such as invoice numbers, amount, spare parts, vendors and upload paperwork related to the service. <br/><br/>                                                                                         
                              (c) Analyze your fleet's per vehicle/service costs. <br/><br/>
                            </p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                             <a href="/assets/screenshots/services.png">
                             <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/services.png" />
                             </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>                                    
                </div> <!-- /row -->
                <hr class="row-divider" />                         
                
                
                <div class="row">
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                                <a href="/assets/screenshots/pm.png" alt="Fleetnext">
                                <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/pm.png" />
                                </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                            <h3> <img src="/assets/alerts.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                            Stay on top of preventive maintenance services
                            </h3>
                            <br/>
                            <p>
                              (a) Setup preventive maintenance (PM) schedule for all vehicle services - both by mileage (e.g. Oil change every 10000 kms) and by time (e.g. Oil change every 1 year). <br/><br/>
                              (b) Subscribe to email notifications to remind you when a vehicle is due for PM service. <br/><br/>
                              (c) Duplicate a vehicle's PM schedule and copy it to other vehicles in the fleet. <br/><br/>                              
                            </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                </div> <!-- /row -->
                <hr class="row-divider" />                
                
                
               <div class="row">
                       <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                                <h3> <img src="/assets/tyre.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                                Track your fleet tyres
                                </h3>
                                <br/>
                                <p>
                                (a) Track every tyre in the fleet - both original equipment fitment (on new vehicles) and replacement (purchased) tyres. <br/><br/>
                                (b) Store tyre make, model, size, position (front axle, rear axle, all position, free rolling), vendor, purchase invoice and payment details. <br/><br/>
                                (c) List currently fitted tyres on a vehicle. Find spare tyres or tyres sent to vendors for remould (recap). <br/><br/>
                                (e) Analyze your fleet's per vehicle/tyre costs. <br/><br/>
                                </p>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                              <a href="/assets/screenshots/tyres.png" alt="Fleetnext">
                              <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/tyres.png" />
                              </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                </div> <!-- /row -->
                <hr class="row-divider" />
                
                
                <div class="row">
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                                <a href="/assets/screenshots/mileage.png" alt="Fleetnext">
                                <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/mileage.png" />
                                </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                            <h3> <img src="/assets/update.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                            Up-to-date vehicle mileage logs
                            </h3>
                            <br/>
                            <p>
                              (a) Update daily mileage (odometer) readings for all vehicles. Supports multiple units including kilometres and miles <br/><br/>
                              (b) Use CSV files to import mileage data in bulk from your existing vehicle GPS tracking systems to avoid manual entry. <br/><br/>
                            </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                </div> <!-- /row -->
                <hr class="row-divider" />
                

                <div class="row">
                       <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                          <h3> <img src="/assets/users.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                          Easy user administration
                          </h3>
                          <br/>
                          <p>
                            (a) Fleetnext is a multi-user collaborative platform. <br/><br/>
                            (b) Add and remove users as your organization evolves. <br/><br/>
                            (c) Each user can be assigned custom permissions for viewing, updating, exporting data across different modules. <br/><br/>
                          </p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                              <a href="/assets/screenshots/users.png" alt="Fleetnext">
                              <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/users.png" />
                              </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                </div> <!-- /row -->
                <hr class="row-divider" />

                
                <div class="row">
                        <div class="grid-4">
                          <div class="service-item gallery">
                              <a href="/assets/screenshots/backup.png" alt="Fleetnext">
                              <img src="/assets/screenshots/tb/backup.png" />
                              </a>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-8">
                          <div class="service-item">
                                 <h3> <img src="/assets/upload.jpg" alt="Fleetnext" />
                                         Export your data
                                 </h3>
                                  <br/>
                                 <p>
                                   (a) Select one or multiple vehicles and download all its data (such as vehicle profile, acquisition, disposal, documents, tyres, service history, preventive maintenance schedule, mileage history) to Microsoft excel file . <br/><br/>
                                   (b) At any given point of time, you can take a backup of your entire account and save a local copy to your computer. <br/><br/>
                                 </p>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                </div> <!-- /row -->

                <%= render :partial => "signup" %>

        </div> <!-- /container -->

</div> <!-- /content -->
	
